DATA CLOUD
Feature Availability in Data Cloud and Customer Data Platform

Your Data Cloud license determines which features are available within your org's Data Cloud. Some features require purchasing an add-on license.

NOTE Limitations of some features vary based on license. To review the functionality of Data Cloud features under the different licenses, see:
Data Cloud Limits and Guidelines
Customer Data Platform Limits and Guidelines
FEATURE	CUSTOMER DATA PLATFORM LICENSES	DATA CLOUD LICENSES


Data Cloud Setup

Manage Data Cloud and connect data sources.

	Available	Available


Data Spaces

Create partitions to organize your data, metadata, and processes into categories, such as brand, region, or department, and then enable users to see and work on data only in the context of their category.

	Requires add-on license	Requires add-on license


Data Streams

Connect to external data sources and ingest data into Data Cloud.

	Available	Available


Data Shares

Share Data Cloud data with external partners.

	Available	Available


Data Lake Objects

Organize ingested data to map the connection between source data and data model objects.

	Available	Available


Data Transforms

Clean, enrich, and manipulate data to prepare for profile unifications, segmentation, and activation.

	Available	Available


Data Modeling

Use Data Cloud’s standard data model to make data interoperable.

	Available	Available


Data Graphs

Provide near real time responses to queries with pre-computed data collected from several data model objects or calculated insights.

	Available	Available


Real-Time Data Graphs and related real-time features

Provide sub-second responses to queries with pre-computed data collected from several data model objects or real-time insights.

	Not Available	Available


Data Explorer

Validate data in data lake objects, data model objects, and calculated insights to ensure that your data and formulas are accurate.

	Available	Available


Identity Resolution

Consolidate data from different sources into a unified view of each customer.

	Available	Available


Profile Explorer

Get a complete view of a Unified Individual’s profile for purposes such as validating unified profiles and checking for profile discrepancies.

	Available	Available


Calculated Insights

Define and calculate multidimensional metrics based on all your Data Cloud data.

	Available	Available


Streaming Insights

Create multidimensional metrics on streaming data.

	Available	Available


Einstein Studio AI Models

Create and use machine learning models externally and connect them to Data Cloud to use different kinds of AI in Salesforce.

	Available	Available


Data Actions and Data Action Targets

Send an alert or an event to a target based on streaming insights and engagement data to trigger an automation or data integration.

	Available	Available


Advertising Integrations

Integrate with the world's largest advertising platform to streamline campaign planning, audience activations, and insights.

	Requires add-on license	Requires add-on license


Segmentation Overall

Break down your data into useful segments to understand, target, and analyze your customers.

	Available	Requires add-on license


Segmentation: Einstein Segments

Use generative AI to build targeted audience segments in Data Cloud with Einstein Segment Creation.

	Available	Requires add-on license


Segmentation: Einstein Lookalike Segments

Grow the reach of your high-value segments using AI-powered Einstein lookalike segments in Data Cloud.

	Not Available	Requires add-on license


Activation and Activation Targets

Publish segments to activation platforms.

	Available	Requires add-on license


Unstructured Data and Search Index Configurations

Connect unstructured data in Data Cloud and create search index configurations to prepare that data for ground search.

	Not Available	Available
